                "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.lp.zone/robertdenby/{size}/514_1.png",
                "created_at": "2017-01-31T19:07:10.410Z",
                "cooked": "<p>Has there ever been a definitive answer as to why this never got any kind of US or European release (outside the demo apparently being in XBox Magazine at some point)?</p>",
