                "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.lp.zone/geop/{size}/23_1.png",
                "created_at": "2017-01-31T19:11:05.849Z",
                "cooked": "<p>Not really. It's most likely either \"this is way too political\" or From just didn't think it'd see much profit? I dunno... I mean, they did give us both Otogi games which have a rather heavy eastern-fantasy setting (if I recall right). A mech game where you play as the US president definitely should've been on the roadmap.</p>",
