                "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.lp.zone/lazodiac/{size}/334_1.png",
                "created_at": "2017-01-31T19:17:33.208Z",
                "cooked": "<p>Metal Wolf Chaos honestly looks kinda clunky gameplay wise, but I feel just the spectacle of it would of made the XBox kind of a must own for people who like ridiculous and silly action games. I feel like the reason they never brought it over HAS to be \"because it's too political\".</p>",
