                "created_at": "2017-01-31T19:47:48.112Z",
                "cooked": "<p>I have no idea how From got the idea to make its two niches \"dark fantasy about dying worlds\" and \"real robots\", but I'm completely on board with this.</p>\n\n<p>Nthing that the voice acting is incredible. &lt;3</p>",
